A photorealistic close-up of a gourmet hamburger being assembled mid-air, with the top bun floating above, revealing layers of fresh lettuce, tomato, and a perfectly grilled patty suspended between artisan brioche buns. The scene is captured against a warm, soft-focus kitchen background with golden hour lighting streaming in from a window. Steam wisps rise from the hot patty, and sesame seeds scatter dynamically in the air around the floating bun. The composition emphasizes the layering and wrapping concept, with each ingredient clearly visible and appetizing, shot from a slight angle to show depth and dimension. Professional food photography style with shallow depth of field.
